"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-zambia-cheers-muzala-samukongas-historic-win-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.7195030908387721, \"rank\": 0.3736365533415457, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbZambia cheers Muzala Samukonga's historic medal at Paris Olympics  Zambia is celebrating a historic achievement as Muzala Samukonga won a bronze medal in the Men's 400 metres at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.7195030908387721, \"rank\": 0.3736365533415457, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zambia is basking in glory after Muzala Samukonga secured a bronze medal in the Men's 400 metres at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old sprinter's outstanding performance has ignited a wave of Zambian pride.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999998293697135, \"rank\": 1.7063029351459037e-07, \"text\": \"Zambian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His achievement is a first for Zambia since 1996, and the whole country is celebrating, according toLusaka Times.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samukonga crossed the finish line with a time of 43.74 seconds, setting a new record.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This impressive result marks Zambia's return to the Olympic medal podium after nearly three decades.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a landmark moment for the nation and its athletics community.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"President Hakainde Hichilema praised Samukonga's dedication and hard work.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hakainde_Hichilema\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hakainde Hichilema\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hakainde_Hichilema\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hakainde_Hichilema\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Muzala's commitment has shone brightly on the global stage,\\\" President Hichilema said.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His achievement fills us with immense pride.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We celebrate this victory with you, Muzala.\\\"\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The joy across Zambia is palpable, according toPulse Sports.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1268, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From bustling cities to quiet towns, people are rejoicing in Samukonga's success.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bronze medal has united the nation, highlighting the talent and potential of Zambian athletes.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999998293697135, \"rank\": 1.7063029351459037e-07, \"text\": \"Zambian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samukonga's victory serves as an inspiration for future generations.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His performance at theParis Olympicshas not only elevated Zambia's standing in athletics but also instilled a renewed sense of hope and ambition among young athletes.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Muzala Samukonga, born on 9 December 2002, is a rising star in track and field.\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Known for his prowess in the 400 metres, Samukonga has quickly made a name for himself.\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At just 19, he clinched gold at the 2022 Commonwealth Games and African Championships.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1969, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Championships_in_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999817364371, \"rank\": 1.0213440476849185e-08, \"text\": \"African Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Championships_in_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Championships_in_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His bronze medal win at the Paris 2024 Olympics, with a time of 43.74 seconds, further solidifies his status as one of Zambia's top athletes.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With this performance, he has set a new national record and showcased Zambia's growing talent on the global stage, according toSuper Sport.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2206, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"African athletes have once again showcased their remarkable talent and determination at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their performances have been nothing short of inspiring, with numerous medals and personal bests achieved across various sports.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As celebrations continue, Samukonga's historic win is a testament to his hard work and the support of his nation.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zambia has reason to be proud, and Muzala Samukonga's name will be remembered for years to come.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999649012359, \"rank\": 3.509855565261031e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations to him for bringing home this prestigious medal and making his country proud.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or by emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.comor sending a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2942, \"end\": 2950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.8756549991577381, \"rank\": 0.14200227368277582, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re